Package net.hudup.core.alg.cf

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MemoryBasedCF
    Note, the abstract class Recommender represents all recommendation algorithm.
    ModelBasedCF
    Note, the abstract class Recommender represents all recommendation algorithm.
    Neighbor2dCF
    This class is also the neighbor collaborative filtering (Neighbor CF) algorithm for users because it extends directly NeighborUserBasedCF.
    NeighborCF
    This class sets up the neighbor collaborative filtering (Neighbor CF) algorithm.
    NeighborItemBasedCF
    This class sets up the neighbor collaborative filtering (Neighbor CF) algorithm for items.
    NeighborUserBasedCF
    This class sets up the neighbor collaborative filtering (Neighbor CF) algorithm for users.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    CFAnnotation
    This annotation indicates that the class to which it is applied is a collaborative filtering (CF) recommendation algorithm.
